8. maja 1948.

114
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:38,957
Ulica Kampanile devet.

115
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:41,472
Napulj, Pijanura.

116
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,393
čekaj.

